            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, strip the <strong>mint leaves</strong> from their stems and&nbsp;chop them roughly</p>\r\n<p>Crumble the <strong>feta&nbsp;</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
