            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1548.-step-6-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>After the 5 min, add the <strong>pea shoots</strong> and most of the <strong>chopped mint</strong> (save some for garnish!)</p>\r\n<p>Transfer everything to a <strong>food processor</strong> and blitz until smooth &ndash; this is your <strong>pea shoot &amp; leek soup</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
